#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:33
msgid ""
"The exact data received depends on the scopes requested and what your "
"identity provider shares."
msgstr ""
"Les données exactes reçues dépendent des portées demandées et de ce que "
"votre fournisseur d'identité partage."

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:38
msgid "How Data Is Stored"
msgstr "Comment les données sont stockées"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:40
msgid "All authentication data is stored server-side in memory."
msgstr ""
"Toutes les données d'authentification sont stockées en mémoire côté "
"serveur."

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:43
msgid "Data is stored in <strong>server memory</strong> (RAM) only"
msgstr ""
"Les données sont stockées uniquement dans la <strong>mémoire du "
"serveur</strong> (RAM)"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:44
msgid ""
"A secure session cookie is sent to your browser (containing only a "
"session ID, not the actual data)"
msgstr ""
"Un cookie de session sécurisé est envoyé à votre navigateur (contenant "
"uniquement un ID de session, pas les données réelles)"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:45
msgid "No database, files, or permanent storage is used"
msgstr "Aucune base de données, fichier ou stockage permanent n'est utilisé"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:46
msgid "All session data is lost when the application restarts"
msgstr "Toutes les données de session sont perdues au redémarrage de l'application"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:47
msgid "Data is cleared when you log out"
msgstr "Les données sont effacées lorsque vous vous déconnectez"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:50
#, python-format
msgid "Sessions expire after %(timeout)s"
msgstr "Les sessions expirent après %(timeout)s"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:52
msgid "Sessions expire when you close your browser"
msgstr "Les sessions expirent lorsque vous fermez votre navigateur"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:59
msgid "Data Sharing"
msgstr "Partage de données"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:61
msgid "Auth Playground does not:"
msgstr "Auth Playground ne :"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:64
msgid "Share your data with third parties"
msgstr "Partage pas vos données avec des tiers"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:65
msgid "Send data to external services"
msgstr "Envoie pas de données vers des services externes"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:66
msgid "Store data permanently"
msgstr "Stocke pas les données de manière permanente"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:67
msgid "Track your usage"
msgstr "Suit pas votre utilisation"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:68
msgid "Use analytics or advertising"
msgstr "Utilise pas d'analyse ou de publicité"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:71
msgid ""
"The only external communication is with your configured identity provider"
" for authentication purposes."
msgstr ""
"La seule communication externe se fait avec votre fournisseur d'identité "
"configuré à des fins d'authentification."

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:76
msgid "Security Considerations"
msgstr "Considérations de sécurité"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:78
msgid "Use only <strong>test accounts</strong>, not real user accounts"
msgstr ""
"Utilisez uniquement des <strong>comptes de test</strong>, pas de vrais "
"comptes utilisateurs"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:79
msgid "Do not use sensitive or production data"
msgstr "N'utilisez pas de données sensibles ou de production"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:80
msgid "Ensure your deployment is properly secured (HTTPS, firewall, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"Assurez-vous que votre déploiement est correctement sécurisé (HTTPS, "
"pare-feu, etc.)"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:81
msgid "Change the default"
msgstr "Changez la valeur par défaut de la"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:81
msgid "environment variable"
msgstr "variable d'environnement"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:86
msgid "Your Rights"
msgstr "Vos droits"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:88
msgid "You can review the source code to understand data handling"
msgstr "Vous pouvez examiner le code source pour comprendre la gestion des données"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:89
msgid "You can modify the application to suit your needs"
msgstr "Vous pouvez modifier l'application pour répondre à vos besoins"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:94
msgid "Identity Provider's Privacy Policy"
msgstr "Politique de confidentialité du fournisseur d'identité"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/policy.html:96
msgid ""
"Your identity provider may have its own privacy policy regarding the data"
" they collect and share. Please review their privacy policy for "
"information about how they handle your data."
msgstr ""
"Votre fournisseur d'identité peut avoir sa propre politique de "
"confidentialité concernant les données qu'il collecte et partage. "
"Veuillez consulter sa politique de confidentialité pour des informations "
"sur la façon dont il gère vos données."

#: src/auth_playground/templates/server_specs.html:2
msgid "Server specifications"
msgstr "Spécifications du serveur"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/server_specs.html:6
#: src/auth_playground/templates/specs.html:12
#, python-format
msgid "Supported specifications (%(count)s)"
msgstr "Spécifications supportées (%(count)s)"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/server_specs.html:17
#: src/auth_playground/templates/specs.html:23
#, python-format
msgid "Unsupported specifications (%(count)s)"
msgstr "Spécifications non supportées (%(count)s)"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/server_specs.html:28
#: src/auth_playground/templates/specs.html:34
#, python-format
msgid "Unknown specifications (%(count)s)"
msgstr "Spécifications inconnues (%(count)s)"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/session.html:6
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "Authentification"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/session.html:7
msgid "Tokens"
msgstr "Jetons"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/session.html:8
msgid "Logout"
msgstr "Déconnexion"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/session.html:12
msgid "Re-authenticate or adjust the request — updates auth_time, acr and amr."
msgstr ""
"Réauthentifiez-vous ou ajustez la requête — met à jour auth_time, acr et "
"amr."

#: src/auth_playground/templates/session.html:21
msgid "Silent refresh — auth_time and acr stay unchanged."
msgstr "Rafraîchissement silencieux — auth_time et acr restent inchangés."

#: src/auth_playground/templates/session.html:30
msgid ""
"Local — this app only; you stay signed in at the provider, so the next "
"sign-in may be silent (SSO)."
msgstr ""
"Local — cette application uniquement ; vous restez connecté chez le "
"fournisseur, donc la prochaine connexion peut être silencieuse (SSO)."

#: src/auth_playground/templates/session.html:77
msgid "Server log out"
msgstr "Déconnexion du serveur"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/session.html:79
msgid ""
"Global — also ends the session at the provider (RP-Initiated Logout), "
"preventing a silent re-login."
msgstr ""
"Global — termine aussi la session chez le fournisseur (RP-Initiated "
"Logout), empêchant une reconnexion silencieuse."

#: src/auth_playground/templates/session.html:85
msgid "No active session"
msgstr "Aucune session active"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/session.html:86
msgid ""
"Sign in to explore OAuth 2.0 and OpenID Connect flows: authentication, "
"token refresh, and logout."
msgstr ""
"Connectez-vous pour explorer les flux OAuth 2.0 et OpenID Connect : "
"authentification, rafraîchissement des jetons et déconnexion."

#: src/auth_playground/templates/specs.html:3
#: src/auth_playground/templates/specs.html:8
msgid "Server Specifications"
msgstr "Spécifications du serveur"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/static-configuration.html:3
msgid "Static configuration"
msgstr "Configuration statique"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/static-configuration.html:6
msgid ""
"If you prefer to configure Auth Playground via environment variables "
"without validating the server first, you can set them directly and "
"restart the application."
msgstr ""
"Si vous préférez configurer Auth Playground via des variables "
"d'environnement sans valider d'abord le serveur, vous pouvez les définir "
"directement et redémarrer l'application."

#: src/auth_playground/templates/static-configuration.html:9
msgid "Create an OAuth client on your provider"
msgstr "Créer un client OAuth sur votre fournisseur"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/static-configuration.html:11
msgid "What configuration details do I need?"
msgstr "Quels détails de configuration ai-je besoin ?"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/static-configuration.html:12
msgid "Configure these URIs in your OAuth client:"
msgstr "Configurez ces URIs dans votre client OAuth :"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/static-configuration.html:24
msgid "Set the following environment variables in a"
msgstr "Définissez les variables d'environnement suivantes dans un fichier"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/static-configuration.html:24
msgid "file or by exporting them in your shell:"
msgstr "ou en les exportant dans votre shell :"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/static-configuration.html:30
msgid "Restart the application"
msgstr "Redémarrez l'application"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:12
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "Objectif"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:14
msgid ""
"Auth Playground is an <strong>educational and demonstration tool</strong>"
" designed to help developers test OAuth2 and OpenID Connect (OIDC) "
"authentication flows. It is intended for:"
msgstr ""
"Auth Playground est un <strong>outil éducatif et de "
"démonstration</strong> conçu pour aider les développeurs à tester les "
"flux d'authentification OAuth2 et OpenID Connect (OIDC). Il est destiné à"
" :"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:18
msgid "Learning and understanding OAuth 2.0 and OpenID Connect protocols"
msgstr "Apprendre et comprendre les protocoles OAuth 2.0 et OpenID Connect"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:19
msgid "Testing integration with identity providers"
msgstr "Tester l'intégration avec les fournisseurs d'identité"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:20
msgid "Demonstrating authentication flows in development environments"
msgstr ""
"Démontrer les flux d'authentification dans les environnements de "
"développement"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:21
msgid "Debugging OIDC implementations"
msgstr "Déboguer les implémentations OIDC"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:26
msgid "Open Source Project"
msgstr "Projet open source"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:28
msgid "Auth Playground is an open source project. You are free to:"
msgstr "Auth Playground est un projet open source. Vous êtes libre de :"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:31
msgid "Use, modify, and distribute the software"
msgstr "Utiliser, modifier et distribuer le logiciel"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:32
msgid "Self-host the application"
msgstr "Auto-héberger l'application"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:33
msgid "Contribute improvements and bug fixes"
msgstr "Contribuer des améliorations et des corrections de bugs"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:34
msgid "Review the source code for security and functionality"
msgstr "Examiner le code source pour la sécurité et les fonctionnalités"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:37
msgid "Please refer to the LICENSE file in the repository for detailed terms."
msgstr ""
"Veuillez vous référer au fichier LICENSE dans le dépôt pour les "
"conditions détaillées."

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:42
msgid "User Responsibility"
msgstr "Responsabilité de l'utilisateur"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:44
msgid "When using Auth Playground, you are responsible for:"
msgstr "Lorsque vous utilisez Auth Playground, vous êtes responsable de :"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:47
msgid "Using only test accounts and non-sensitive data"
msgstr "Utiliser uniquement des comptes de test et des données non sensibles"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:48
msgid "Securing your deployment appropriately for your environment"
msgstr "Sécuriser votre déploiement de manière appropriée pour votre environnement"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:49
msgid "Configuring environment variables correctly"
msgstr "Configurer correctement les variables d'environnement"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:50
msgid "Understanding the security implications of your setup"
msgstr "Comprendre les implications de sécurité de votre configuration"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:51
msgid "Complying with your identity provider's terms of service"
msgstr "Respecter les conditions d'utilisation de votre fournisseur d'identité"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:56
msgid "No Warranty"
msgstr "Aucune garantie"

#: src/auth_playground/templates/tos.html:58
msgid ""
"This software is provided \"as is\" without warranty of any kind, express"
" or implied. Use at your own risk."
msgstr ""
"Ce logiciel est fourni « en l'état » sans garantie d'aucune sorte, "
"expresse ou implicite. Utilisez-le à vos propres risques."

